      "question": "Wir ____ Käse.",
      "options": ["esse", "essen", "trinken", "lernen"],
      "correctAnswer": "essen",
      "explanation": "wir uses the -en ending (essen)!"
    },
    {
      "type": "multiple_choice",
      "question": "Wie spricht man eine fremde Person höflich an?",
